# Specify how to check and ignore uncolored shapes on DPT layers during 
	# DEF out and stream out. If true or 1, checks uncolored shapes on all 
	# DPT layers; if false or 0, doesn't do check; if metal_only, only checks 
	# uncolored shapes on metal layers, uncolored shapes on cut layers are 
	# ignored. It's automatically set to metal_only for TSMC N5 and below nodes.